      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In science, business, policy, and other fields, a careful item-by-item comparison of two or more comparable characteristics, alternatives, processes, products, qualifications, sets of data, or other features in order to draw an authoritative conclusion.</Note_Text>
